{
 "name": "RPlog_Third_Battle_of_Kessel",
 "title": "The Third Battle of Kessel",
 "summary": "Rear Admiral Danik Kreldin's Imperial squadron -- the Star Destroyer Tormentor, the VSD Renegade, and the Interdiction picket Oppressor -- is running battle drills over the prison world of Kessel when a New Republic task force, spearheaded by the Star Destroyer Crusader and a wing of Corellian gunships, jumps into the system. Badly outnumbered, Kreldin scrambles his bombers and fighters, signals Selene for reinforcements, and pours fire into the Crusader while Republic bombers under Darenak (Razor 1) and Seppi, harried by a lone A-Wing, press their attack runs. The fight becomes a grinding capital-ship slugfest: the Crusader's shields are battered down and its hull pounded by the Tormentor and Oppressor even as the gunships under Oppenhiemer dart along the edges lobbing missiles. The Oppressor takes heavy damage, but the Imperial line holds; the Crusader is left a battle-scarred wreck and the Republic gunships break off, leaving the Tormentor and Renegade undamaged as the engagement winds down.",
